    <item>
      <title>安巴尼对 Petchem 和税收的依赖未达到利润预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ambani-s-reliance-misses-profit-estimate-on-petrochemicals-drag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼(Mukesh Ambani)领导的信实工业有限公司(Reliance Industries Ltd.)公布的季度利润低于预期，原因是石化业务持续疲软，税收增加抵消了消费部门的增长和其他收入的大幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ambani-s-reliance-misses-profit-estimate-on-petrochemicals-drag</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 13:40:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>吉尔丹任命前高盛高管为主席，以对抗维权投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gildan-taps-ex-goldman-exec-as-chair-in-last-stand-against-activist-investor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大服装制造商 Gildan Activewear Inc. 表示，数名董事将在几天内离职，高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 的一名前高管将担任董事长，这是董事会为说服投资者不要支持激进股东的计划而做出的最后努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gildan-taps-ex-goldman-exec-as-chair-in-last-stand-against-activist-investor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应忧虑持续，铜价每吨达 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/copper-nears-10-000-as-investors-bet-on-rising-global-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价每吨接近 10,000 美元，创下两年新高，因为投资者继续押注矿商将难以满足对这种领头工业金属需求激增的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/copper-nears-10-000-as-investors-bet-on-rising-global-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:05:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
