      <title>美元的长期统治给市场敲响了警钟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/dollar-s-extended-supremacy-is-a-stark-wake-up-call-for-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球金融市场正在遭遇一种他们在 2024 年并未押注的力量：强势美元卷土重来，而且看起来将持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/dollar-s-extended-supremacy-is-a-stark-wake-up-call-for-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 00:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
